{{ja-pron|ね|acc=0|acc_ref=DJR,NHK}}

====Noun====
{{ja-noun|ね}}

# {{defdate|from late 900s}} a [[sound]], [[voice]]
# {{defdate|from 712}} the [[cry]] of an [[animal]]

=====Usage notes=====
''Ne'' is used for relatively soft sounds and voices that appeals to human emotions, as opposed to the [[音#Japanese:_oto|''oto'']] reading.

